name: Enter The Bureaucrat
Lore: 'Even the most effective of operations can be easily mired under the Republic''s plethora of procedural red tape.',
Text: 'If you just lost more than 2 Force to a Force drain, deploy on opponent''s location. You lose no more than 1 Force from Force drains here. At any time, you may place Immediate Effect in Used Pile to draw two cards from top of Reserve Deck.',
